21:37.875 --> 21:38.959
- You're a succubus.

21:39.041 --> 21:41.792
- In Korea, we call it
a kumiho.

21:41.875 --> 21:43.959
A nine-tailed fox spirit.

21:44.041 --> 21:45.166
- And you killed 100 men.

21:45.250 --> 21:47.458
- It is my nature.

21:47.542 --> 21:48.875
What is your excuse?

21:52.917 --> 21:55.250
When I have sex

21:55.333 --> 21:56.625
and my lover climaxes,

21:56.709 --> 22:00.458
my nine tails attach to him,
taking his life force.

22:00.542 --> 22:03.959
That is how I am able
to see their entire lives

22:04.041 --> 22:07.458
up till their deaths.

22:07.542 --> 22:09.333
The last time with you,
when my tails came out--

22:09.417 --> 22:11.291
- When?

22:11.375 --> 22:14.125
When am I supposed to die?

22:14.208 --> 22:16.208
- I don't know.
- But it's gonna happen soon?

22:16.291 --> 22:17.750
Right?
That's why you're here.

22:17.834 --> 22:20.542
- I'm not sure.
- But you saw how it happened.

22:20.625 --> 22:23.625
Right?
- No.

22:23.709 --> 22:25.458
I'm sorry.

22:27.125 --> 22:29.667
