29:36.333 --> 29:37.917
- What?
- Behind you.

29:38.000 --> 29:39.583
There's--there's--

29:39.667 --> 29:42.709
[coughing]

29:42.792 --> 29:43.875
- You okay?

29:43.959 --> 29:47.417
