30:12.917 --> 30:14.417
<i>♪ You had better stop</i>
<i>this knocking at the door ♪</i>

30:14.500 --> 30:15.542
<i>- ♪ Let me in ♪</i>

30:15.625 --> 30:16.959
<i>- ♪ Stop that knocking,</i>
<i>stop that knocking ♪</i>

30:17.041 --> 30:18.500
<i>♪ Stop that knocking,</i>
<i>stop that knocking ♪</i>

30:18.583 --> 30:20.250
<i>♪ You had better stop</i>
<i>this knocking at the door ♪</i>

30:20.333 --> 30:21.625
<i>- ♪ Let me in ♪</i>

30:21.709 --> 30:24.667
[distant siren wailing]

30:35.250 --> 30:37.875
- Dee was here,
but she snuck out again.

30:39.208 --> 30:40.375
- Did you cheat on my mama?

30:47.792 --> 30:50.250
- I had desires,
but I never acted on 'em.

30:53.083 --> 30:55.166
Not until after she was gone.

30:55.250 --> 30:58.250
[distant siren wailing]

31:18.125 --> 31:20.542
When I was a boy, 8 years old,

31:20.625 --> 31:22.583
pastor of my church, he...

31:26.083 --> 31:28.583
Got caught with another man
in the park.

31:31.625 --> 31:33.208
He said it was just a rumor.

31:33.291 --> 31:35.542
[scoffs]

31:35.625 --> 31:38.250
Palm Sunday morning,

31:38.333 --> 31:39.375
police came in there

31:39.458 --> 31:42.250
and snatched him off the pulpit
in handcuffs,

31:42.333 --> 31:44.667
like he was some
perverted demon or something.

31:46.000 --> 31:48.083
Next thing we hear, they done
put him in some asylum

31:48.166 --> 31:50.041
and cut out half his brain.

31:50.125 --> 31:53.083
<i>[somber music]</i>

31:53.166 --> 31:56.041
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:56.125 --> 31:58.917
I chose a life
over a damn asylum.

31:59.041 --> 32:02.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:02.959 --> 32:06.417
Or a jail cell,
or being found dead

32:06.500 --> 32:10.041
in a bathroom
of some public park.

32:10.125 --> 32:13.458
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:13.542 --> 32:17.208
Your mama lost everyone
in the riots.

32:17.291 --> 32:19.208
Massacre, really.

32:19.291 --> 32:26.291
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:27.333 --> 32:29.208
We both just wanted a family.

32:29.291 --> 32:32.250
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:32.333 --> 32:35.083
That's what our love
was built on.

32:35.166 --> 32:36.500
A'ight, yeah,
it wasn't romantic,

32:36.583 --> 32:39.166
but familial love
is the strongest kind.

32:41.542 --> 32:44.250
Well, you'll see one day.

32:44.333 --> 32:45.917
God bless you to have kids.

32:46.000 --> 32:49.291
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:49.375 --> 32:52.291
[electricity humming]

32:52.375 --> 32:59.375
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:03.709 --> 33:06.667
- Leti's pregnant.

33:06.750 --> 33:09.667
She hasn't told me yet.

33:09.750 --> 33:11.125
Aunt Hippolyta's
not the only one

33:11.208 --> 33:12.959
who went through the portal.

33:13.041 --> 33:15.959
<i>[uneasy music]</i>

33:16.041 --> 33:17.291
I went to the future.

33:17.375 --> 33:24.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:29.750 --> 33:30.959
That's my son.

33:31.041 --> 33:36.083
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:36.166 --> 33:37.959
- Heavenly Father...

33:41.041 --> 33:45.417
I know You said

33:45.500 --> 33:48.667
we were all meant
to go through trials

33:48.750 --> 33:50.417
and tribulations.

33:53.417 --> 33:57.083
But this magic...

33:59.750 --> 34:03.166
That's haunting us...

34:03.250 --> 34:06.125
and testing us...

34:06.208 --> 34:07.917
it's like the devil.

34:10.959 --> 34:14.625
That part, You left out.

34:18.959 --> 34:22.583
And now, God,

34:22.667 --> 34:26.333
the man that I love...

34:26.417 --> 34:28.542
I'm begging You, God.

34:28.625 --> 34:30.542
I'm begging You.

34:30.625 --> 34:33.208
Please, God,

34:33.291 --> 34:35.542
please...

34:35.625 --> 34:38.375
protect him.

34:38.458 --> 34:41.667
Put Your shield of armor
around him

34:41.750 --> 34:44.125
as he says that spell, God.

34:49.792 --> 34:51.125
[sighs]

34:54.000 --> 34:56.250
[groans]

34:56.333 --> 34:59.417
And please, God,

34:59.500 --> 35:02.583
extend Your grace
to Emmett's family.

35:02.667 --> 35:04.375
To Mamie.

35:04.458 --> 35:06.750
[sniffles]

35:06.834 --> 35:08.041
[sighs]

35:08.125 --> 35:11.417
In Your mighty name, I pray.

35:11.500 --> 35:14.750
Amen.

35:14.834 --> 35:17.583
[exhales sharply]

35:17.667 --> 35:20.583
- I didn't figure you
as a woman of faith.

35:20.667 --> 35:23.583
<i>[tense music]</i>

35:23.667 --> 35:27.041
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:27.125 --> 35:31.041
- I wasn't.

35:31.125 --> 35:33.583
But I died

35:33.667 --> 35:36.417
and was resurrected.

35:36.500 --> 35:38.667
- That wasn't a miracle.

35:38.750 --> 35:40.625
It was magic.

35:40.709 --> 35:44.375
- Are they really so different?

35:44.458 --> 35:47.792
Walking on water,
curing the blind,

35:47.875 --> 35:51.291
raising the dead.

35:51.375 --> 35:54.250
- Perhaps my father
considered himself godlike

35:54.333 --> 35:57.291
when he resurrected you,
but he was just a mortal,

35:57.375 --> 35:58.959
confused that being powerful

35:59.041 --> 36:01.417
and being able to manipulate
those around him

36:01.500 --> 36:03.959
made him more.

36:04.041 --> 36:07.458
Most men with god complexes
wanna live in heaven,

36:07.542 --> 36:09.250
but not hell,

36:09.333 --> 36:13.250
failing to understand
that God is both.

36:13.333 --> 36:16.166
- [scoffs]

36:16.250 --> 36:19.000
Is that what you want?

36:19.083 --> 36:21.625
To be God?

36:21.709 --> 36:22.834
- I'm sure
you didn't summon me here

36:22.917 --> 36:24.375
to find out what I want.

36:24.458 --> 36:31.458
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:34.583 --> 36:37.000
- These are negatives
of Titus's pages.

36:37.083 --> 36:39.417
They're yours.
- If?

36:39.500 --> 36:42.083
- If you make
Atticus invulnerable.

36:43.792 --> 36:44.875
- No.

36:44.959 --> 36:49.333
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:49.417 --> 36:52.208
Not for Atticus.

36:52.291 --> 36:53.333
For you.

36:53.417 --> 37:00.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:14.834 --> 37:15.917
- Wait.

37:16.000 --> 37:23.000
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:33.375 --> 37:37.083
- [speaking Language of Adam]

37:37.166 --> 37:38.375
- [cries out]

37:38.458 --> 37:42.959
[gasping]

37:43.041 --> 37:44.917
- Mark of Cain.

37:45.000 --> 37:47.917
My father's
invulnerability spell.

37:48.000 --> 37:49.875
I was the first to realize

37:49.959 --> 37:51.875
you could use it
to heal someone.

37:51.959 --> 37:58.959
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:00.375 --> 38:03.291
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

38:03.375 --> 38:05.625
