<i>- ♪ Let me in ♪</i>

38:59.291 --> 39:00.542
<i>♪ Let me in ♪</i>

39:00.625 --> 39:02.625
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

39:12.583 --> 39:14.291
<i>♪ Let me in, let me in ♪</i>

39:14.375 --> 39:16.125
<i>[music growing]</i>

39:22.250 --> 39:24.041
<i>♪ Let me in, let me in ♪</i>

39:24.125 --> 39:25.208
<i>♪ Let me in ♪</i>

39:25.291 --> 39:32.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:33.208 --> 39:34.542
<i>- ♪ Stop that knocking,</i>
<i>stop that knocking ♪</i>

39:34.625 --> 39:35.875
<i>♪ Stop that knocking,</i>
<i>stop that knocking ♪</i>

39:35.959 --> 39:38.041
<i>♪ You had better stop</i>
<i>this knocking at the door ♪</i>

39:38.125 --> 39:39.750
<i>- ♪ Let me in ♪</i>

39:43.291 --> 39:46.917
[siren wailing]

39:47.000 --> 39:48.375
- Should've never
gave Christina

39:48.458 --> 39:51.375
the keys to Hiram's machine.

39:51.458 --> 39:52.959
- It doesn't matter.

39:54.417 --> 39:55.792
She can't use it.

39:55.875 --> 39:57.875
It's broken.

39:57.959 --> 40:00.041
- So what?
Hippolyta.

40:00.125 --> 40:02.166
What, she trapped
in the future?

40:02.250 --> 40:04.208
- Maybe.

40:04.291 --> 40:07.500
It was chaotic.

40:07.583 --> 40:09.291
White folks were rioting.

40:11.959 --> 40:13.166
I was only there for a second

40:13.250 --> 40:14.875
before the woman in the hood
came in,

40:14.959 --> 40:16.250
shoved a book in my hand,

40:16.333 --> 40:18.250
pushed me back
through the portal.

40:18.333 --> 40:20.792
- With the robotic arm.

40:20.875 --> 40:22.500
[chuckles]

40:26.166 --> 40:30.083
"George Freeman's writings
were inspired

40:30.166 --> 40:31.750
"by his heroic father,

40:31.834 --> 40:34.166
a Korean War vet."

40:36.834 --> 40:38.041
You read it?

40:39.208 --> 40:42.959
- It's our family story.

40:43.041 --> 40:44.792
Some of the details
are different.

40:46.375 --> 40:48.000
Christina's a man.

40:48.083 --> 40:51.542
Uncle George survives Ardham.

40:51.625 --> 40:55.375
And Dee's a boy named Horace.

40:55.458 --> 40:57.583
<i>[uneasy music]</i>

40:57.667 --> 40:58.959
But there's enough
similarities to it,

40:59.041 --> 41:01.917
makes me think
there's some truth to it.

41:02.000 --> 41:04.375
- Please tell me
there's a happy ending.

41:06.709 --> 41:09.000
- Christina sacrifices me

41:09.083 --> 41:11.792
to become immortal

41:11.875 --> 41:13.333
on the autumnal equinox.

41:13.417 --> 41:20.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:22.000 --> 41:24.333
- That's in five days.

41:24.417 --> 41:27.208
- I know casting a spell
can kill me,

41:27.291 --> 41:29.291
but I also know I gotta take
every chance I can

41:29.375 --> 41:30.834
to live for my son.

41:30.917 --> 41:37.500
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:37.583 --> 41:39.125
What should I do?

41:39.208 --> 41:45.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:45.959 --> 41:47.291
- You know, son...

41:47.375 --> 41:51.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:51.959 --> 41:54.000
I always thought
my death would come

41:54.083 --> 41:56.500
at the end of a white man's
bullet or a rope.

41:56.583 --> 41:59.834
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:59.917 --> 42:02.208
Magic's so much more jazz.

42:02.291 --> 42:05.959
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:06.041 --> 42:09.709
Didn't you tell me that
part of casting was intention?

42:09.792 --> 42:13.000
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:13.083 --> 42:14.250
- Yes, sir.

42:16.750 --> 42:18.792
- Well, it's my intention
to do whatever I can

42:18.875 --> 42:22.250
to save my son and my grandson.

42:24.250 --> 42:26.875
Even if it kills me.

42:26.959 --> 42:30.208
- We don't know
how much magic they know.

42:30.291 --> 42:32.375
We can't just come at them.

42:32.458 --> 42:35.583
And her pioneering has made
this bitch a local celebrity.

42:38.250 --> 42:39.458
- Is my mama dead?

42:42.291 --> 42:45.083
- Probably.

42:45.166 --> 42:47.333
- What did you do to me
with your spit?

42:48.250 --> 42:49.333
- Couldn't have you
telling anybody

42:49.417 --> 42:50.625
about our little chats.

42:52.583 --> 42:55.125
- What happens if it gets me?

42:58.291 --> 43:01.792
<i>[ominous music]</i>

43:01.875 --> 43:03.458
- [grunts]

43:06.166 --> 43:08.083
I can remove it.

43:08.166 --> 43:09.917
The curse.

43:10.000 --> 43:13.709
But you have to do something
for me first.

43:13.792 --> 43:14.875
You know what an orrery is?

43:14.959 --> 43:17.291
- Yeah, I know
what an orrery is,

43:17.375 --> 43:20.125
and my mama's name
is Hippolyta!

43:20.208 --> 43:22.125
It's Greek, asshole.

43:22.208 --> 43:23.625
- [laughs]

43:25.709 --> 43:28.625
You bring me the one
from the Winthrop house,

43:28.709 --> 43:31.750
and I'll save you
from whatever's following you.

43:31.834 --> 43:38.750
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:38.834 --> 43:40.542
- Fuck you, pig.

43:40.625 --> 43:44.083
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:44.166 --> 43:46.625
And it fucking stinks in here!

43:46.709 --> 43:50.917
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:51.000 --> 43:52.959
- To hell with the girl.

43:53.041 --> 43:55.500
She's already dead.

43:55.583 --> 43:59.166
It's time to get
what belongs to me.

43:59.250 --> 44:01.291
<i>- I am here today</i>
<i>to acknowledge and represent</i>

44:01.375 --> 44:02.333
<i>the African-American girls</i>

44:02.417 --> 44:03.917
<i>whose stories don't make</i>
<i>the front page</i>

44:04.000 --> 44:05.291
<i>of every national newspaper.</i>

44:05.375 --> 44:06.375
<i>[cheers and applause]</i>

44:06.458 --> 44:08.959
<i>Whose stories don't lead</i>
<i>on the evening news.</i>

44:09.041 --> 44:13.583
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

44:13.667 --> 44:15.458
<i>I represent</i>
<i>the African-American women</i>

44:15.542 --> 44:16.959
<i>who are simply statistics</i>

44:17.041 --> 44:18.709
<i>instead of vibrant,</i>
<i>beautiful girls</i>

44:18.792 --> 44:20.417
<i>full of potential.</i>

44:20.500 --> 44:23.458
<i>For far too long, these names,</i>
<i>these Black girls and women,</i>

44:23.542 --> 44:25.291
<i>have been just numbers.</i>

44:25.375 --> 44:26.500
[bones crack]

44:26.583 --> 44:29.834
<i>I'm here to say "Never again"</i>
<i>for those girls too.</i>

44:29.917 --> 44:31.333
<i>I am here to say</i>

44:31.417 --> 44:33.709
<i>that everyone should value</i>
<i>those girls too.</i>

44:33.792 --> 44:37.000
<i>♪ ♪</i>

44:37.083 --> 44:38.667
- [screams]

44:38.750 --> 44:40.792
<i>- To honor the girls,</i>
<i>the women of color,</i>

44:40.875 --> 44:42.458
<i>who are murdered</i>
<i>at disproportionate rates</i>

44:42.542 --> 44:43.792
<i>in this nation.</i>

44:43.875 --> 44:44.875
<i>I urge each of you</i>

44:44.959 --> 44:46.834
<i>to help me write</i>
<i>the narrative for this world</i>

44:46.917 --> 44:49.125
<i>and understand</i>
<i>so that these girls and women</i>

44:49.208 --> 44:50.291
<i>are never forgotten.</i>

44:50.375 --> 44:53.458
- [panting]

44:53.542 --> 44:55.959
<i>♪ ♪</i>

44:56.041 --> 44:58.208
[screams]

44:58.291 --> 45:04.500
<i>♪ ♪</i>

45:04.583 --> 45:08.333
- "In flood, he water

45:08.417 --> 45:11.041
shall be reprieved from death."

45:13.792 --> 45:16.208
That don't make any sense.

45:16.291 --> 45:18.709
- Let me see.

45:18.792 --> 45:20.542
Where?

45:20.625 --> 45:23.542
"In flood water,

45:23.625 --> 45:25.417
he shall be reprieved
from death."

45:25.500 --> 45:28.875
You switched up the words.

45:28.959 --> 45:32.583
- Yeah, I tend
to do that sometimes.

45:34.250 --> 45:37.583
- What you mean, "sometimes"?

45:37.667 --> 45:39.166
- I'm dyslexic, boy.

45:42.000 --> 45:43.375
- Since when?

45:43.458 --> 45:44.917
- Since I've been a boy.

45:48.458 --> 45:50.667
- Shit, any other secrets
you keeping from me?

45:52.625 --> 45:53.667
Jeez.

45:55.166 --> 45:56.250
- Come on, man,
let's just do this

45:56.333 --> 45:57.709
before I lose my damn nerve.

45:57.792 --> 46:00.709
<i>[ominous music]</i>

46:00.792 --> 46:03.709
[siren wailing]

46:03.792 --> 46:10.792
<i>♪ ♪</i>

46:15.542 --> 46:18.959
[speaking Language of Adam]

46:52.208 --> 46:53.875
Amen.

46:56.041 --> 46:58.000
Well, shit, it can't hurt!

46:58.083 --> 47:05.041
<i>♪ ♪</i>

47:11.083 --> 47:12.250
You feel anything?

47:12.333 --> 47:16.458
<i>♪ ♪</i>

47:16.542 --> 47:17.583
- No.

47:23.250 --> 47:24.291
You?

47:32.750 --> 47:34.667
Fuck.

47:34.750 --> 47:41.750
<i>♪ ♪</i>

47:44.375 --> 47:46.750
Didn't work.

47:56.041 --> 47:58.125
- You ever done
anything like this before?

47:58.208 --> 48:01.208
- No.
It's my first time.

48:01.291 --> 48:02.375
- You sure?

48:02.458 --> 48:05.417
- You have your money.

48:06.959 --> 48:09.875
[speaking Language of Adam]

48:09.959 --> 48:14.709
<i>♪ ♪</i>

48:14.792 --> 48:17.709
- [grunts]
- [groaning]

48:17.792 --> 48:20.750
<i>[tense music]</i>

48:20.834 --> 48:25.917
<i>♪ ♪</i>

48:26.000 --> 48:27.959
- [grunts]
- [groans]

48:28.041 --> 48:32.000
[wheezing]

48:32.083 --> 48:35.166
[grunting]

48:35.250 --> 48:37.000
- Get her up!
Get her up.

48:37.083 --> 48:41.917
- [moaning]

48:42.000 --> 48:43.917
- [grunts]
- [wheezing]

48:44.000 --> 48:46.000
- [grunts]
- [moans]

48:46.083 --> 48:48.458
- [grunts]

48:48.542 --> 48:50.083
[grunts]

48:50.166 --> 48:53.125
- [groaning]

48:53.208 --> 48:59.083
<i>♪ ♪</i>

48:59.166 --> 49:02.625
[gunshots]

49:02.709 --> 49:06.625
<i>♪ ♪</i>

49:06.709 --> 49:09.625
[moaning]

49:09.709 --> 49:16.667
<i>♪ ♪</i>

49:37.000 --> 49:38.792
- Why would anyone wanna die
like that?

49:38.875 --> 49:43.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

49:50.041 --> 49:50.959
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

49:51.041 --> 49:55.291
- [gasping and moaning]

49:55.375 --> 49:57.792
[wheezing]

49:57.875 --> 50:01.291
[whimpering]

50:01.375 --> 50:05.000
[sobbing laughs]

50:05.083 --> 50:07.500
<i>- ♪ Don't know why ♪</i>

50:07.583 --> 50:10.208
- [laughs]

50:10.291 --> 50:14.667
<i>- ♪ There's no sun</i>
<i>up in the sky ♪</i>

50:14.750 --> 50:17.041
<i>♪ Stormy weather ♪</i>

50:17.125 --> 50:19.041
- [sighs]

50:19.125 --> 50:22.667
<i>- ♪ Since my man and I ♪</i>

50:22.750 --> 50:26.875
<i>♪ Ain't together ♪</i>

50:26.959 --> 50:29.625
<i>♪ Keeps raining ♪</i>

50:29.709 --> 50:32.500
<i>♪ All the time ♪</i>

50:32.583 --> 50:34.750
- Are these from Emmett's wake?

50:37.291 --> 50:41.959
<i>- ♪ Life is bare ♪</i>

50:42.041 --> 50:43.750
- Did you see him?

50:54.458 --> 50:55.875
Mamie was brave enough

50:55.959 --> 50:57.792
to show the world
what they did to her son,

50:57.875 --> 51:02.166
and I wasn't even brave enough
to take a few damn pictures.

51:02.250 --> 51:04.709
- Choosing what was best
for yourself in that moment

51:04.792 --> 51:07.500
was a different kind
of bravery.

51:07.583 --> 51:10.959
You can't feel guilty
for protecting yourself first.

51:12.917 --> 51:14.291
- [sighs]

51:22.417 --> 51:24.333
I'm pregnant.

51:25.458 --> 51:27.750
- Oh.

51:27.834 --> 51:29.291
Damn it, Leti.

51:30.166 --> 51:31.291
Oh, you've really gone

51:31.375 --> 51:33.333
and gotten yourself
into it now.

51:33.417 --> 51:35.208
- [scoffs]

51:35.291 --> 51:37.083
Don't even know
the half of it, Ruby.

51:37.166 --> 51:38.917
- You should've stayed your ass
at Marvin's

51:39.000 --> 51:40.834
instead of following that man
to Ardham.

51:42.291 --> 51:44.125
Yeah, I know all about magic

51:44.208 --> 51:46.667
and how George really died.

51:47.834 --> 51:50.250
- That white man
you staying with?

51:50.333 --> 51:53.583
- Only a man some of the time.

51:53.667 --> 51:54.792
Christina Braithwhite.

51:54.875 --> 51:57.542
<i>[uneasy music]</i>

51:57.625 --> 51:59.792
- She got you spying on us
or something?

51:59.875 --> 52:01.583
- How can you even ask me that?

52:01.667 --> 52:02.583
- Because she came to me

52:02.667 --> 52:04.291
and tried to get me to do
the same damn thing.

52:04.375 --> 52:05.667
She's playing you, Ruby.

52:05.750 --> 52:07.542
- No, I'm getting
exactly what I want.

52:07.625 --> 52:09.583
- And what is that?

52:09.667 --> 52:12.041
- Magic.

52:12.125 --> 52:16.083
She gave me a potion that can
turn me into a white lady.

52:16.166 --> 52:18.291
Yeah.
- [scoffs]

52:18.375 --> 52:20.458
- And I finally got that job
at Marshall Field's,

52:20.542 --> 52:21.959
and you know what I learned?

52:22.041 --> 52:24.625
I don't wanna be white.

52:24.709 --> 52:27.583
I'm just sick of forgiving
every space that I enter

52:27.667 --> 52:29.625
'cause it's not for me.

52:29.709 --> 52:32.959
I wanna create my own space.

52:33.041 --> 52:34.166
I can do that with magic.

52:34.250 --> 52:37.291
Christina's gonna teach me.

52:37.375 --> 52:38.750
- Ruby...

52:38.834 --> 52:40.959
- Leti, you need
to get up here now!

52:41.041 --> 52:46.333
<i>♪ ♪</i>

52:46.417 --> 52:49.625
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

52:49.709 --> 52:56.458
<i>♪ ♪</i>

53:06.583 --> 53:08.667
[banging on door]

53:08.750 --> 53:10.667
- Letitia Lewis.

53:10.750 --> 53:13.000
We have a warrant
to search the premises.

53:13.083 --> 53:15.667
<i>[tense music]</i>

53:15.750 --> 53:18.542
- What the fuck?

53:18.625 --> 53:21.125
[banging on door]

53:21.208 --> 53:28.208
<i>♪ ♪</i>

53:39.000 --> 53:40.834
[banging on door]
- Go back to your rooms.

53:40.917 --> 53:42.667
- Leti, let me handle this.

53:42.750 --> 53:44.041
I don't want your baby
born in jail.

53:44.125 --> 53:45.417
[banging on door]

53:45.500 --> 53:46.792
- Shit.

53:49.959 --> 53:53.667
- What is this about, Officer?

53:53.750 --> 53:54.917
- We got a tip...
- Move.

53:55.000 --> 53:57.375
- That known Nation of Islam
radicals were organizing here

53:57.458 --> 53:59.542
in retaliation for Emmett Till.

53:59.625 --> 54:01.458
- That's bullshit.
- Leti.

54:01.542 --> 54:02.709
[forcefield clangs]

54:02.792 --> 54:09.792
<i>♪ ♪</i>

54:14.291 --> 54:15.875
- Let's go.

54:15.959 --> 54:20.667
<i>♪ ♪</i>

54:20.750 --> 54:21.917
- What the hell just happened?

54:22.000 --> 54:24.750
- Our house is protected.
That motherfucker knows magic.

54:24.834 --> 54:26.125
- Well, now he knows
that you do too.

54:26.208 --> 54:29.792
[gunfire]
[both screaming]

54:32.000 --> 54:33.083
- Get down!

54:33.166 --> 54:35.125
[glass shattering]
[gunfire]

54:35.208 --> 54:37.375
[both screaming]

54:37.458 --> 54:40.375
<i>[uneasy music]</i>

54:40.458 --> 54:47.458
<i>♪ ♪</i>

54:48.500 --> 54:49.875
[metal scrapes]

54:49.959 --> 54:53.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

54:53.500 --> 54:56.500
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

54:56.583 --> 55:03.542
<i>♪ ♪</i>

55:10.875 --> 55:12.792
- [screams]

55:12.875 --> 55:18.625
<i>♪ ♪</i>

55:18.709 --> 55:21.625
[screaming]

55:21.709 --> 55:27.750
<i>♪ ♪</i>

55:28.750 --> 55:30.250
[distant gunfire]

55:30.333 --> 55:33.250
[glass shattering]

55:33.333 --> 55:36.250
<i>[ominous music]</i>

55:36.333 --> 55:42.834
<i>♪ ♪</i>

55:42.917 --> 55:44.959
- [distant and echoing]
Leti! Get down!

55:45.041 --> 55:52.041
<i>♪ ♪</i>

56:00.917 --> 56:02.000
- [screaming]

56:02.083 --> 56:03.166
- Dee!

56:03.250 --> 56:04.291
Dee!

56:04.375 --> 56:05.500
[grunting]

56:05.583 --> 56:06.834
I'm coming!

56:06.917 --> 56:09.667
- [screaming]

56:09.750 --> 56:10.667
- Dee!

56:10.750 --> 56:13.834
- [screaming]

56:15.166 --> 56:17.166
Let me go!

56:17.250 --> 56:18.333
- What's wrong, baby?

56:18.417 --> 56:21.458
- [crying out]

56:24.250 --> 56:27.166
[screaming]

