<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

56:30.250 --> 56:33.542
<i>♪ ♪</i>

56:33.625 --> 56:36.625
[siren wailing]

56:43.792 --> 56:47.875
[gunfire]

56:47.959 --> 56:54.959
<i>♪ ♪</i>

56:59.834 --> 57:01.792
- Get your fucking hands up!

57:01.875 --> 57:03.208
Hey!

57:03.291 --> 57:05.917
I said
get your fucking hands up!

57:06.000 --> 57:07.542
- Get your hands up, boy!

57:07.625 --> 57:12.417
<i>♪ ♪</i>

57:12.500 --> 57:13.917
- No!

57:14.000 --> 57:20.083
<i>♪ ♪</i>

57:20.166 --> 57:22.291
No!
No!

57:22.375 --> 57:25.458
[gunshot]

57:25.542 --> 57:28.542
[bullet whistles]

57:32.500 --> 57:35.500
[monster growls]

57:37.834 --> 57:40.875
